# ============================================================
# NordicWings — Environment Variables
# Copy this file to .env for local development.
# On Railway: add each variable in the Railway dashboard under
#   Your Project → Variables → Add Variable
# ============================================================

# ── Stripe (payment processing) ──────────────────────────────
STRIPE_SECRET_KEY=sk_live_...your_stripe_secret_key...

# ── Duffel (real flight search & booking) ────────────────────
DUFFEL_API_KEY=duffel_live_...your_duffel_key...

# ── Sky Scrapper / RapidAPI (flight search fallback) ─────────
RAPIDAPI_KEY=...your_rapidapi_key...

# ── Flight Reminder Emails ────────────────────────────────────
# NordicWings can automatically send "Your flight is tomorrow!"
# reminder emails to customers the day before their flight.
#
# STEP 1: Make sure your Gmail account has 2-Step Verification ON
#         Google Account → Security → 2-Step Verification → Turn On
#
# STEP 2: Create a Gmail App Password (NOT your regular password)
#         Google Account → Security → 2-Step Verification
#         → Scroll to "App passwords" → Create → Select "Mail"
#         → Copy the 16-character password shown
#
# STEP 3: Add these two variables on Railway:
GMAIL_USER=your-email@gmail.com
GMAIL_PASS=xxxx xxxx xxxx xxxx

# That's it! NordicWings will now send beautiful reminder
# emails every morning at 08:00 Helsinki time.
# ============================================================
